      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, representing the highest standard of automotive care. The exterior paint is entirely flawless, with a deep, mirror-like shine and no scratches, dents, or chips of any kind. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with leather that looks and smells like new and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a complete and documented history. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and driven only in ideal conditions.",
