    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S features the high-revving 3.4L M97 flat-six mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. Engineered for optimal weight distribution, the mid-engine layout offers a low polar moment of inertia for razor-sharp turn-in. This example is equipped with the Sport Chrono package and PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management), ensuring a versatile damping profile. The vehicle has undergone a preventive water pump replacement and a recent top-end inspection to verify valve train integrity. While the exterior shows light stone chipping on the front fascia, the chassis remains rigid and the throttle response is instantaneous. A mechanically sound driver's car with a clean DME overrev report.",
